# Trivy ignore file (.trivyignore)
#
# SR12 (control-plane dependency audit) blocks HIGH/CRITICAL findings.
# This file carries temporary ignores with justification and an owner for
# each entry. Every entry MUST be time-boxed and reviewed on each
# quarterly security audit cycle.
#
# Format: one CVE per line; comments start with '#'.

# --- web/admin / lodash transitive dep ------------------------------
# CVE-2026-4800 affects lodash 4.17.23 (shipped as a transitive dep of
# some web/admin devDependencies). The fixed version is 4.18.0. The
# data-plane binary does not bundle lodash; the vulnerability is only
# exploitable at npm-dev time (template compilation with untrusted
# input). Upgrading transitively requires bumping the top-level tooling
# (vite / eslint), tracked in a separate chore(web-admin) ticket.
# Review by: 2026-07-31 (quarterly audit).
CVE-2026-4800
